{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙随陶方商队冒雨行军，白夷少女秀夷追踪而来，告知灰胡八百马贼将在打石谷伏击的消息，并与项少龙露水情缘。项少龙将情报告知陶方，陶方判断魏人窦良为内奸，赠越国匕首命其刺杀。项少龙用计在密林中诱杀窦良。当晚野火宴后，项少龙献计连夜赶路以甩掉马贼探子。次日藏营休息，陶方将侍妾婷芳氏赠予项少龙。婷芳氏讲述被丈夫卖掉的悲惨身世，项少龙心生怜意。陶方传来消息已杀追踪贼子，灰胡暂时被甩掉，但马贼擅长追踪，危机未解。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人家跟踪你两天两夜哩！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快逃！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我叫秀夷，和我回白夷山吧！若你随那些赵人到邯郸去，定被灰胡那群马贼杀死。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "text": "你在说什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 49
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "几天前，我们族内的人收到消息，灰胡和他的八百马贼准备在打石谷伏击赵人，抢他们的女人和马匹，你若跟去，一定会给杀死的，他们比焦毒那些人厉害得多。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "text": "我自有方法应付他们。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我也知你不会弃友逃生，人家不逼你了。可是秀夷告诉你这么有用的情报，你要怎样酬谢人家？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "text": "除铜钱外，什么都可以。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "人人都说我生得美，你同意吗？人家还不知你叫什么名字哩！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "text": "我叫项少龙！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 71
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这样是否更美呢？族中的男人都爱看我的身体。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "text": "过来！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_yi_ren_nv",
      "speaker_name": "秀夷",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "从来都只是男人求我，今天却是我求你。来吧！情郎！我已两天没有回家，你再不出来人家可要入营找你了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "陶爷到邯郸的路线必然非常保密，知道的人没有多少个，所以灰胡若知道你会经过打石谷，必是因有内奸向他提供消息了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我真的没看错你，不但一表人才，生具奇相，还智勇兼备。好！只要我陶方一日仍当权，必然不会亏待你。",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "内奸定是窦良，有两个原因使我肯定是他，首先他曾借故离队两天，该是去与灰胡见面；其次，知道我们行程路线的几个人中，只有他是魏人，魏人都不可靠的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "魏人既不可靠，为何你又用他呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 105
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你长居山区，自然对中原的形势不了解。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "我真的很想知道！",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这要由三家分晋说起，那是整个时代的分水岭，之前还说尊王攘夷，分晋后变成魏、韩和我们赵国，没有人再把周室放在眼里。若说以前的局势像是一条平静的河川，现在却是奔腾的湍流。十年间的变化，足抵得以前的一百年，没有本领的人，将会被淘汰。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "现在秦国是否最强大的国家？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "秦自用了卫国贵族公孙鞅的改革政策后，的确富强起来，五年前还攻破周室，但亦犯了众怒，被我国大将乐乘、庆舍大破秦军，魏更在三年前攻占秦国在东方的重要据点陶郡，秦国声势已大不如前。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！我要你帮我把窦良这奸贼杀了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 127,
      "line_end": 129
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "这个包在我身上，不过假若杀错人，岂非亲者痛、仇者快？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是新来的人，窦良仍未摸清你的底子，你可用言语试探他，包他中计。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "凡魏人均属可杀，我也是最近才知他是魏人，早打算这次任务完成后再不用他，岂知他竟先发制人。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "手脚干净点，事后我会对人说派他到别处办事。这匕首来自越国的铸剑名匠，吹发可断，就送给你，让它饱饮魏贼的血。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "魏人曾占据我们的国都邯郸达两年之久，全赖齐国出面才迫使魏人退兵，但仍有很多魏人留在邯郸充当走狗间谍，窦良正是这类人，你下手时切不可留情。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今天这批女孩的质素非常好，项兄要不要向陶爷讨两个来玩玩，他很看得起你呢！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_shan",
      "text": "何处找来这么多可人儿？她们不觉得被人当货物般售卖是很凄惨的事吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项兄不是山区人吗？女人若非货物是什么呢？如给卖到穷乡僻壤，一个女人应付全家上下十多个男人，那才真惨哩！现在她们可到城市去，幸运的被大户人家看中，穿金戴银，不知多么风光哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 168,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_shan",
      "text": "窦良哪里去了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shan",
      "speaker_name": "李善",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他自恃是头儿，刚拣了个最美的娘儿携到帐内去，你说他要干什么？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dou_liang",
      "text": "有胆便一个人随我来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dou_liang",
      "text": "窦大哥，我是灰胡派来协助你的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dou_liang",
      "text": "现在计划有变，灰胡决定不在打石谷下手，教我来通知窦大哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "窦良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "灰胡在弄什么鬼，不在打石谷还有什么更好的地方？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "窦良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "站在哪里说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_dou_liang",
      "text": "窦大哥疑心太重了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dou_liang",
      "speaker_name": "窦良",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "陶方这老狐狸相当厉害，我怎能不小心点。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙你到那些女席拣拣看，看得入眼的便带几个入帐作乐，绝不用不好意思。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "陶爷有没有兴趣连夜赶路，教敌人的探子明早忽然发现失去我们整营人马呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "小女子婷芳氏，奉陶爷之命在路途上服侍项爷。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "坐起来吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "谁舍得把你卖出来的？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "是小女子的丈夫！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "什么？竟有这么不懂怜香惜玉的男人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷的说话真有趣，和其他人都不同。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "他是否不行了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "什么是'不行'啊？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "即是说没有本事和女人行房欢好的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "并不是为了这问题，而是因他早有十多个妻子，她们都排挤小女子，又在背后中伤小女子，说小女子爱用眼睛去勾引其他男人，于是把小女子卖了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "那你有没有勾引男人？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "开始时没有，后来便有了。因为小女子希望有比他更强的男人来解救人家，只要瞧不到他和他的妻子，什么牺牲小女子也愿接受。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷和其他男人不同，他们一见到小女子便急着脱掉衣服扑上来，只有项爷会和我这么说话，小女子很感激哩！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "text": "东面好像有道清溪，我想到那里洗个冷水浴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让小女子伺候项爷入浴。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那是小女子最大的荣幸。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "若少龙满意这个女人，让她以后跟你好哩！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "探子有什么消息回来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙猜得不错，有三个贼子在追踪我们，已给杀了，灰胡应暂时被我们甩掉。不过仍不可大意，马贼擅长追踪，兼之我们行速缓慢，迟早会给他们赶上来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "吃过东西后，我们立即起程，看看能赶多少路，给我十来个人，我会把车马的行迹完全抹掉，还可以制造一点假象，教贼人摸错路子。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这事全赖你了，好好享受吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ting_fang_shi",
      "speaker_name": "婷芳氏",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项爷！以后我就是你的人了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 341
    }
